{{message/zh-CN|哇！你突然看不到自己了。|你在通常状态下喝下了隐形药水。|Gee!  All of a sudden, you can't see yourself.}}
{{message/zh-CN|由于某些原因，你感觉自己的存在为人所知了。|你喝下了被诅咒的隐形药水。|For some reason, you feel your presence is known.}}
{{message/zh-CN|哇！你突然能看见透明的自己。|你在具有看见隐形特质的情况下喝下了隐形药水。|Gee!  All of a sudden, you can see right through yourself.}}
{{message/zh-CN|真荒诞！你能够看见透明的自己。|你在处于[[幻觉]]状态的情况下喝下了隐形药水。|Far out, man!  You can't see yourself.}}
{{message/zh-CN|真荒诞！你能够看见透明的自己。|你在拥有看见隐形，且处于幻觉状态的情况下喝下了隐形药水。|Far out, man!  You can see right through yourself.}}
{{message/zh-CN|你片刻有一种离奇的感觉，然后消退了。|你在已经具有隐形特质，或处于失明状态，或穿戴木乃伊绷带的情况下喝下了隐形药水。|You have a peculiar feeling for a moment, then it passes.}}
{{message/zh-CN|你片刻有一种普通的感觉，然后消退了。|同上，但你同时还处于幻觉状态。|You have a normal feeling for a moment, then it passes.}}

{{message/zh-CN|突然你看不到<怪物>了。|一只怪物喝下了隐形药水并进入隐形状态。|Suddenly you cannot see <monster>.}}
{{message/zh-CN|<怪物>的身体呈现出奇怪的透明。|同上，但你拥有看见隐形特质。|<monster>'s body takes on a strange transparency.}}
{{message/zh-CN|<怪物>的身体呈现出普通的透明。|同上，但你同时处于幻觉状态。|<monster>'s body takes on a normal transparency.}}
{{message/zh-CN|由于某些原因，<怪物>的存在被你得知了。||For some reason, <monster's> presence is known to you.}}
{{message/zh-CN|你感觉对隐形的<怪物>恼火。|一只怪物喝下了被诅咒的隐形药水。|You feel aggravated at the invisible <monster>.}}
{{message/zh-CN|你受到愤怒的刺激而恢复了意识。|同上，你从失去意识的状态中恢复。|Aggravated, you are jolted into full consciousness.}}

{{message/zh-CN|你在一瞬间内看不到你自己了！|你在未处于隐形状态的情况下，吸入了隐形药水的蒸汽。|For an instant you couldn't see yourself!}}
{{message/zh-CN|你在一瞬间内能看见透明的自己！|同上，但你同时具有看见隐形特质。|For an instant you could see right through yourself!}}

==Variants==
{{translation/zh-CN|n}}
===SLASH'EM===
In [[SLASH'EM]], dipping an item in a potion of invisibility will turn it [[Invisible item (SLASH'EM)|invisible]].

Two potions of invisibility are placed randomly in the open area of [[Grund's Stronghold]] at level creation.

===UnNetHack===
In [[UnNetHack]], the fake "throne room" in [[Asmodeus' Lair (UnNetHack)|Asmodeus' Lair]] has a potion of invisibility in each of its four corners.

===SpliceHack===
In [[SpliceHack]], the fake "throne room" in [[Asmodeus' Lair (SpliceHack)|Asmodeus' Lair]] has a potion of invisibility in each of its four corners as in UnNetHack.

===EvilHack===
In [[EvilHack]], [[agent]]s are always generated with potions of invisibility.

===SlashTHEM===
In [[SlashTHEM]], in addition to SLASH'EM details, the [[Ninja (role)|Ninja]] starts each game with a blessed potion of invisibility.

Making a potion of invisibility via [[chemistry set]] uses up three charges.

